{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id909c0941-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5813"},"text":"§ 5813.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Report on overall assistance and economic cooperation strategy","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id909c0942-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Requirement for submission","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"As soon as practicable after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"October 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", the coordinator designated pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5812/a"},"text":"section 5812(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall submit to the Congress a report on the overall assistance and economic cooperation strategy for the independent states of the former Soviet Union that is required to be developed pursuant to paragraph (1) of that section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id909c0943-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Assistance plan","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The report submitted pursuant to subsection (a) shall include a plan specifying—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id909c0944-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of the funds authorized to be appropriated for fiscal year 1993 by chapter 11 of part I of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2295"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2295","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] proposed to be allocated for each of the categories of activities authorized by section 498 of that Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2295"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2295","children":[],"tail":"] and to carry out "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5821"},"text":"section 5821 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (relating to American Business Centers), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5823"},"text":"section 5823 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (relating to export promotion activities and capital projects), and subchapter III of this chapter (relating to the Democracy Corps);"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id909c0945-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of other funds made available for fiscal year 1993 to carry out the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2151","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] proposed to be allocated for assistance under that Act for the independent states of the former Soviet Union; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id909c0946-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5813/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of funds available for fiscal year 1993 under the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2151","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] that are proposed to be made to each agency to carry out activities for the independent states under that Act or this Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id909c0947-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/511/tI/s103"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–511, title I, § 103","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3323"},"text":"106 Stat. 3323","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id909c0948-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id909c0949-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id909c094a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Foreign Assistance Act of 1961, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-09-04"},"text":"Sept. 4, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/424"},"text":"75 Stat. 424","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 32 (§ 2151 et seq.) of this title. Chapter 11 of part I of the Act is classified generally to part XI (§ 2295 et seq.) of subchapter I of chapter 32 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"section 2151 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in subsec. (b)(3), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/511"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–511","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3320"},"text":"106 Stat. 3320","children":[],"tail":", known as the Freedom for Russia and Emerging Eurasian Democracies and Open Markets Support Act of 1992 and also as the FREEDOM Support Act. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5801"},"text":"section 5801 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
